 And in a split second, Tyson was gone.

526
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:04,780
 I could not see him anywhere.

527
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:07,220
 And this is in Deerfield.

528
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:09,580
 It's not like there's like crowds and like buildings.

529
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:12,420
 This is like Deerfield, suburban Chicago.

530
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:13,660
 But he's nowhere to be seen

531
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:16,620
 and it felt like time stood still forever.

532
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:19,220
 And I could hear my heart beating so fast

