00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:07,540
 or we're competing with those around us.

663
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:13,440
 Because after all, that's what society tells us to do.

664
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:16,040
 But I wanna mark that actually,

665
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:20,040
 that in Mark, Jesus is also talking to children

666
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:22,680
 'cause he invites a child in their midst.

667
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:27,680
 So the children might not be the active, direct listeners,

668
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:29,160
 but they're listening.

669
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,840
 As you know, if you ever have kids,

670
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:32,960
 you can say one thing and they hear it

671
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:33,880
 and they'll repeat it.

672
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:35,480
 But you'll say 10,000 other things

673
00:32:35,500 --> 00:32:37,500
 that you want them to say and they won't.

674
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:39,780
 Unless that's just my kids.

675
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:44,140
 And I wonder when these children are listening

676
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:47,220
 to what Jesus is saying to the disciples,

677
00:32:47,220 --> 00:32:48,860
 if they feel comforted.

678
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:50,660
 Because as children, they have no power.

679
00:32:50,660 --> 00:32:52,060
 They have no choice.

680
00:32:52,060 --> 00:32:54,140
 But what Jesus is saying is,

681
00:32:54,140 --> 00:32:57,860
 they're so important that all of you need to be like them.

682
00:32:57,860 --> 00:33:02,340
 And maybe some of us,

683
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:05,380
 we don't relate to judging Pharisees.

684
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:09,880
 We don't relate to maybe disciples who are quarreling.

685
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:12,840
 Do we relate to children?

686
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:14,560
 Do we feel helpless?

687
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:16,120
 Do we feel confused?

688
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:17,280
 Do we feel lost?

689
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:19,480
 Do we feel inexperienced?

690
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:22,560
 But yet, our God tells us

691
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:25,020
 that children are the most beautiful thing.

692
00:33:25,020 --> 00:33:31,380
 And what we see here is that bottom row, agency.

693
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:35,640
 We get to have that agency to look at these stories

694
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,960
 in a zoomed out way.

